{"id":10982,"date":"2024-01-24T18:55:30","date_gmt":"2020-06-24T13:25:30","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?p=10982"},"modified":"2024-02-08T21:50:40","modified_gmt":"2024-02-08T16:20:40","slug":"low-floor-bed-designs","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bedroom-interiors\/low-floor-bed-designs\/","title":{"rendered":"Get A Good Night\u2019s Sleep: The Best Low-Floor Bed Designs For Your Home"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p><em>Transform your bedroom into a daily retreating oasis by choosing a low-floor bed that defines your bedroom\u2019s overall mood and look.<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>A bed is probably one of the first pieces of furniture that you buy when you are setting up your home, validated by the fact that we spend about 1\/3rd of our lives sleeping on it. Within this context, low-floor beds have become quite a popular option among buyers since they are closer to the floor (around 18\u201d from the ground with a mattress included). They also don\u2019t require any box springs for additional support.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Low-floor beds offer many health-related, aesthetic and functional benefits to homeowners. On the health front, low-floor beds keep you fit because of mild\/deep stretching involved to get out of it (Note: old people or people with weak knees can overlook this one), help you fight off dizziness quickly and cool down your body temperature if you are a hot sleeper.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>On the functional front, low-floor beds give you high-quality comfort and sleep on a pocket-friendly budget with just a soft mattress and a few throw cushions. However, it does not provide you with any storage options. It is also safe for small children who tend to fall over from the bed.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>On the aesthetic front, low-floor beds give you a sense of spaciousness in the room by being minimalistic and sleek in its design, and add a modern touch to your room.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Also, here\u2019s a quick guide that will help you make an informed decision to choose the right low-floor bed for yourself.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><strong>Height of the bed<\/strong> &#8211; It should typically correlate with your height so that it is easy for you to sit in and step out of it. It should be at least 15 inches above the floor along with the mattress<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Size of the bed<\/strong> &#8211; Single-Person Bed | Double Bed | King-Size Bed | Queen-Size Bed<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Level of comfort<\/strong> &#8211; Since your bed is a lifetime investment so don\u2019t compromise on the comfort that it should provide you, even if you have to pay a little over your fixed budget. Research and actively test-rest on it before buying it<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>The structure and dimensions of your room<\/strong> &#8211; Keep a note on the dimensions and layout of your room before you start looking out for the perfect low-floor bed. You should be able to visualize the entire bedroom theme in your mind.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Material of the bed<\/strong> &#8211; Natural Wood | HDF Ply | MDF Ply | Compressed Wood | Pinewood | Polished Wood.&nbsp;<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>The budget &#8211; Work through your finances before you start the quest, as there is always a bed for every budget<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Now, let\u2019s dive into some of the most popular low-floor bed designs, so that you can relax and recharge yourself in minutes.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Blast Of Colours On This Low Floor Bed Design<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>This light-toned wooden low-floor bed is an ideal choice for a child\u2019s bedroom. It makes the room look more spacious and airy. For a playful and lively vibe, team up the low floor bed with a brightly coloured bedspread and throw pillows. You can also throw an interesting rug on the hardwood floor to tie everything together.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/24184314\/blast-of-colours-low-floor-bed-design.jpg\" alt=\"Light-toned wooden low-Floor bed designs with a blast of colours surrounding it\" class=\"wp-image-10988\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/24184314\/blast-of-colours-low-floor-bed-design.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/24184314\/blast-of-colours-low-floor-bed-design-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/24184314\/blast-of-colours-low-floor-bed-design-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/24184314\/blast-of-colours-low-floor-bed-design-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Also, check out <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/guides\/bedroom-colour-combinations\/\">Bedroom Colour Combinations<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Customise your bed and enjoy up to 25 year warranty\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/08210059\/customise-your-bed-enjoy-up-to-25-year-warranty.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Traveller&#8217;s Haven With This Low Floor Bed Design<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>What can ever go wrong with the grey-blue classic look? This black low floor bed pairs harmoniously with the grey-themed interiors and the pair of hanging lights installed on each side. Satisfy your inner traveller by adding a handcrafted steel world map on the wall and a bright blue bean bag for a laid-back feel.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/24184913\/traveller-low-floor-double-bed-design.jpg\" alt=\"Low floor bed designs in black with the grey-themed interior and handcrafted steel world map on the wall\" class=\"wp-image-10994\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/24184913\/traveller-low-floor-double-bed-design.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/24184913\/traveller-low-floor-double-bed-design-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/24184913\/traveller-low-floor-double-bed-design-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/24184913\/traveller-low-floor-double-bed-design-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">All That Bling<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>This light grey low-floor bed lends a bold and sophisticated statement to the room\u2019s landscape. The disco-themed hanging lights and table accessories add the required bling into the space while not being too overwhelming. The wide windows balance out the entire look. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/24184416\/bling-low-floor-bed-designs.jpg\" alt=\"Low floor double bed in light grey colour with disco-themed hanging lights\" class=\"wp-image-10989\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/24184416\/bling-low-floor-bed-designs.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/24184416\/bling-low-floor-bed-designs-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/24184416\/bling-low-floor-bed-designs-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/24184416\/bling-low-floor-bed-designs-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Artistic Beauty<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>This frameless, double-layered low-floor bed is all what you would need for a peaceful sleep. It is so comfortable that you will doze off in seconds. The spaced-out effect <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bedroom-interiors\/bedroom-wooden-wall-panel-designs\/\">wooden panelling<\/a> on the back wall creates visual drama and the bottled light ceiling lights makes the room stand out distinctively. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/24184212\/artistic-beauty-low-floor-double-bed.jpg\" alt=\"Low floor king-size bed which is frameless, double layered with wooden panelling on back\" class=\"wp-image-10987\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/24184212\/artistic-beauty-low-floor-double-bed.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/24184212\/artistic-beauty-low-floor-double-bed-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/24184212\/artistic-beauty-low-floor-double-bed-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/24184212\/artistic-beauty-low-floor-double-bed-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Elegance Personified<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Experience true luxury with this low-floor bed that lies within a frame extending across the wall right upto the ceiling. It oozes elegance and class into the room and the cozy papasan chair acts as an extension for reading your favourite books.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/24184612\/personified-low-floor-king-size-bed.jpg\" alt=\"Wooden low floor bed whose frame extend across the wall right up to the ceiling.\" class=\"wp-image-10991\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/24184612\/personified-low-floor-king-size-bed.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/24184612\/personified-low-floor-king-size-bed-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/24184612\/personified-low-floor-king-size-bed-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/24184612\/personified-low-floor-king-size-bed-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Bedroom interior design with a bed that fits just right\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/08180953\/bedroom-interior-design-with-a-bed-that-fits-just-right.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Relax By The Sea Side <\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>If you are dreaming of relaxing by the sea side, you can go in for this king-sized low-floor bed. The sea-green tufted headboard will remind you of the calming waters and the brown mattress will remind you of the warm sand beneath your toes. The artistic wall piece, the dual-hued accent wall and the light wooden floor harmoniously pair with each other to complete this visual story.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/24184813\/seaside-low-floor-double-bed-designs.jpg\" alt=\"Light wooden low floor king-size bed with sea-green tufted headboard and brown mattress\" class=\"wp-image-10993\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/24184813\/seaside-low-floor-double-bed-designs.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/24184813\/seaside-low-floor-double-bed-designs-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/24184813\/seaside-low-floor-double-bed-designs-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/24184813\/seaside-low-floor-double-bed-designs-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Also, check out <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bedroom-interiors\/headboard-designs\/\">Headboard Designs<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Scandinavian Minimalism<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>This soft-cushioned low-floor bed is the perfect representation of \u2018less is more\u2019. The design is such that it extends into becoming a study table by the large window. The wood panel on one side and the textured wall on the other provides the optimal balance between tradition and modernity.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/24184713\/scandinavian-minimalism-low-floor-bed-height.jpg\" alt=\"Soft-cushioned low floor double bed design with study table by the large window \" class=\"wp-image-10992\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/24184713\/scandinavian-minimalism-low-floor-bed-height.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/24184713\/scandinavian-minimalism-low-floor-bed-height-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/24184713\/scandinavian-minimalism-low-floor-bed-height-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/24184713\/scandinavian-minimalism-low-floor-bed-height-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Your Zen Corner<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>This low-floor bed mimics the Japanese-style floor bed. The natural-toned colours of the frame and mattress along with green potted plants and bright panel lights creates a zen hideaway. It offers you the ideal environment for a peaceful meditation session. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/24185012\/zen-corner-bed-frame-low-to-floor.jpg\" alt=\"Japanese-style low floor double bed designs with natural-toned colours\" class=\"wp-image-10995\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/24185012\/zen-corner-bed-frame-low-to-floor.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/24185012\/zen-corner-bed-frame-low-to-floor-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/24185012\/zen-corner-bed-frame-low-to-floor-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/24185012\/zen-corner-bed-frame-low-to-floor-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Hope this blog has inspired you to explore more low-floor bed designs for your home. Say goodbye to cranky, achy and sleepless nights now!&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Explore More About <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/interior-design\/bedroom-design\/\">Bedroom Design By DesignCafe<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"row blog-form\">\n\t<div class=\"offset-lg-3 col-lg-6 bg-light\">\n<fieldset class=\"field-set\">\n<!-- <legend align=\"left\"> -->\n                    \n    <h3 class=\"widget-title text-dark text-center mb-0\">Unwind In Your Personal Sanctuary<\/h3>\n  \n \n     <p class=\"text-center text-dark mt-0\"> Get 20% extra space with modular interiors<\/p>\n    <!-- <\/legend> -->\n<form id=\"blogContactUsFormMain\" action=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/get_quote_action.php\" method=\"post\"\n    novalidate=\"novalidate\">\n    <div class=\"form-group\">\n        <input type=\"text\" class=\"form-control\"  name=\"your-name\" placeholder=\"Enter your name*\" \/>\n        <!-- <span class=\"sales-txt-label\" id=\"labeltxt\">Enter your name*<\/span>  -->\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"form-